## Format

The orchestrator parses headings and bullet items. Sections may be
omitted if not applicable. The file may be edited at any time; the
orchestrator reads the latest version on each sync.

If the sub-kit goes idle (no active task), set Current task to
`idle` and clear the ETA / Notes sections. Don't delete the file —
the orchestrator uses its presence as the signal that this sub-kit
participates in the protocol.
